The changelist from the original Log4Vala are shown below.
- Log4Vala statically links with binaries instead of .so library format.
- Changed the directory structure of the test code for Log4Vala.
- Added license text to Log4Vala test code header.
- refresh_filehandle()@src/log4vala/Appender/FileAppender.vala
  Added process to create if the log file save directory does not exist.
